        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer76656149&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer76656149" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2727013786096987155">To say this was a book about chivalry, the best of knights committed rape, murder, stayed away from battle in order to spend more time with a princess, and put the empire at risk by staying away from the battle. Another knight committed adultery. I can see that what is considered chivalrous behavior has changed since 1490 when this was written.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


