Paris and Rome, and the mysterious events that lead to their deaths&amp;mdash;the humbly devout Joan is continually challenged, and perhaps titillated, by Don Toni&amp;rsquo;s impious personality, his defiance of church authority, and his scandalous affairs. Partly condemning and partly admiring his devilish mentor, the pure-minded Don Joan&amp;rsquo;s lurid &amp;ldquo;biography&amp;rdquo; of the Bearns is a testament to the eternal attractiveness of the libertine, and the lengths to which we go in justifying our own worst impulses.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"6940268100573890662\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'17_book_2424949\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"6GUd1jWBb6waiBsHn7yzMDbk9n4dYXFZ8ibXPM1dW1MdNo6WLb8UBr1CbLh7wLdzwmhe/1qGWD76n6Q39OhPng==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"2424949\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"17_book_2424949\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/13641489-tirant-lo-blanc\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'s